dc_title_s: An International Travel map Beijing scale 1:23,250
dc_description_s: Panel title. "[copyright] Weller Cartographic Services Ltd." Includes notes, 2 lists of legation information, coverage map, and col. ill. Insets: Gugong (Palace) Museum plan -- Yiheyuan (Summer palace) plan. "This map was created on an Apple Macintosh Centris 650. 70 megabytes of RAM was added ... Adobe Illustrator 5.5 was used as the drawing software. An Abaton 300/colour scanner ... was used to create map templates from the manuscripts." Publisher's no.: 685.
